<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>FLC Registration System</title>
    <!-- Link to Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- Add meta viewport -->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md bg-dark navbar-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">FLC Registration System</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <!-- <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">About</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Contact</a>
                </li> -->
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Daftar AOP</h1>
        <h5>Selamat datang di formulir pendaftaran AOP, ketika anda menyelesaikan pendaftaran anda dapat 
            mendownload tagname anda dan mengubahnya secara mandiri jika ada perubahan pada tagname anda.<br><br>
            Pastikan nomor whatsapp dan email anda aktif karena link download dan link pengubahan data 
            akan dikirimkan ke nomor/email tersebut, terima kasih Tuhan Yesus Memberkati
        </h5>
        <form method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/register" id="registration-form">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="full_name">Nama Lengkap</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="full_name" name="full_name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="born_date">Tanggal Lahir</label>
                <input type="date" class="form-control" id="born_date" name="born_date" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="city">Kota Asal</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="city" name="city" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="phone_number">Nomor Whatsapp</label>
                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone_number" name="phone_number" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="position_at_church">Posisi di Gereja</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="position_at_church" name="position_at_church" required>
                    <option value="">--Select--</option>
                    <option value="Gembala Sidang">Gembala Sidang</option>
                    <option value="Pengerja">Pengerja</option>
                    <option value="Pelayan">Pelayan</option>
                    <option value="Jemaat">Jemaat</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="tshirt_size">Ukuran Kaos</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="tshirt_size" name="tshirt_size" required>
                    <option value="">--Select--</option>
                    <option value="S">S</option>
                    <option value="M">M</option>
                    <option value="L">L</option>
                    <option value="XL">XL</option>
                    <option value="XXL">XXL</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="blazer_size">Ukuran Jas</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="blazer_size" name="blazer_size" required>
                    <option value="">--Select--</option>
                    <option value="S">S</option>
                    <option value="M">M</option>
                    <option value="L">L</option>
                    <option value="XL">XL</option>
                    <option value="XXL">XXL</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="profile_picture">Foto Anda di Tag Name Nanti</label>
                <input type="file" class="form-control-file" id="set_file" accept="image/*" required>
                <input hidden type="text" id="profile_picture" name="profile_picture" required>
                <img width="500px" src="" alt="" id="preview" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="quotes_words">Kata Mutiara</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="position_at_church" name="quotes_words" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Register</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
